      "text": "one giant wall for no reason."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 97898.0,
      "end_time": 99867.0,
      "text": "Not to mention  the astronomical cost"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 99867.0,
      "end_time": 102536.0,
      "text": "of staffing    and maintaining the wall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 102536.0,
      "end_time": 104271.0,
      "text": "which taxpayers like you    and your children"
