      "text": "Looks like our CGI budget ran out."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 126593.0,
      "end_time": 129162.0,
      "text": "Okay, yes,   it may be expensive"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 129162.0,
      "end_time": 130364.0,
      "text": "but that doesn't change the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 130364.0,
      "end_time": 132366.0,
      "text": "that once we build it,  it will work."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 132366.0,
      "end_time": 133667.0,
      "text": "Not like you think."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 133667.0,
      "end_time": 135736.0,
      "text": "Increasing security at the border"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 135736.0,
      "end_time": 137604.0,
      "text": "will never stop illegal immigration."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 137604.0,
      "end_time": 139039.0,
      "text": "Why not?"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 139039.0,
      "end_time": 140474.0,
      "text": "No one's getting passed me."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 140474.0,
      "end_time": 142476.0,
      "text": "Yes, they are because   it's estimated that"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 142476.0,
      "end_time": 145846.0,
      "text": "between 27% and 40% of all   undocumented immigrants"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 145846.0,
      "end_time": 148615.0,
      "text": "in America came here on planes."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 148615.0,
      "end_time": 150851.0,
      "text": "(plane passing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 150851.0,
      "end_time": 152719.0,
      "text": "I forgot about planes."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 152719.0,
      "end_time": 154788.0,
      "text": "These immigrants didn't  sneak over the border."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 154788.0,
      "end_time": 157524.0,
      "text": "They came here legally    through passport control,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 157524.0,
      "end_time": 159259.0,
      "text": "then just overstayed their visas."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 159259.0,
      "end_time": 161061.0,
      "text": "And guess what? A border wall's"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 161061.0,
      "end_time": 166834.0,
      "text": "not gonna stop 'em because, reminder..."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 166834.0,
      "end_time": 168135.0,
      "text": "You fools!"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 168135.0,
      "end_time": 170637.0,
      "text": "You forgot about planes!"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 170637.0,
      "end_time": 174374.0,
      "text": "We always forget about planes!"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 174374.0,
      "end_time": 177110.0,
      "text": "Even by your estimate   of visa overstays,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 177110.0,
      "end_time": 179313.0,
      "text": "the wall would still stop about half"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 179313.0,
      "end_time": 181381.0,
      "text": "of America's 11 million   illegal immigrants."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 181381.0,
      "end_time": 182683.0,
      "text": "No, it wouldn't."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 182683.0,
      "end_time": 184618.0,
      "text": "'Cause of a little something called circular flow."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 184618.0,
      "end_time": 185619.0,
      "text": "Here, I'll show you."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 185619.0,
      "end_time": 186887.0,
      "text": "(dog yelps)"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 186887.0,
      "end_time": 191058.0,
      "text": "For decades, immigration to the U.S. was a circular flow."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 191058.0,
      "end_time": 192693.0,
      "text": "People would come, work for a bit"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 192693.0,
      "end_time": 195629.0,
      "text": "and then after they were done,   go home to their families."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 195629.0,
      "end_time": 198265.0,
      "text": "Meet Douglas Massey."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 198265.0,
      "end_time": 199633.0,
      "text": "Thanks, Adam."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 199633.0,
      "end_time": 202069.0,
      "text": "My arms were getting pretty    tired waiting for my cue."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 202069.0,
      "end_time": 203303.0,
      "text": "He's a professor at Princeton"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 203303.0,
      "end_time": 205506.0,
      "text": "and a pioneering    researcher on this topic."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 205506.0,
      "end_time": 207674.0,
      "text": "When the Reagan, Bush   and Clinton administrations"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 207674.0,
      "end_time": 208809.0,
      "text": "drastically increased border"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 208809.0,
      "end_time": 209943.0,
      "text": "enforcement in response"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 209943.0,
      "end_time": 211011.0,
      "text": "to public opinion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 211011.0,
      "end_time": 213013.0,
      "text": "they stopped that circular flow."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 213013.0,
      "end_time": 216416.0,
      "text": "Not by keeping people out,  but by keeping people in."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 216416.0,
      "end_time": 218552.0,
      "text": "(Douglas)   As it got harder and harder  to go back and forth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 218552.0,
      "end_time": 219953.0,
      "text": "people crossing   the border decided"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 219953.0,
      "end_time": 226827.0,
      "text": "they were much better off    just staying in the U.S."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 226827.0,
      "end_time": 227961.0,
      "text": "If I go back to Mexico now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 227961.0,
      "end_time": 230831.0,
      "text": "he won't let me back   in the U.S."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 230831.0,
      "end_time": 235636.0,
      "text": "I guess I'll just stay here...   in Tucson."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 235636.0,
      "end_time": 237905.0,
      "text": "Ironically, this increase  in border enforcement"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 237905.0,
      "end_time": 239773.0,
      "text": "caused the number of undocumented immigrants"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 239773.0,
      "end_time": 243544.0,
      "text": "living in the United States  to skyrocket by 248%."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 243544.0,
      "end_time": 245779.0,
      "text": "It's counterintuitive, but building a wall"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 245779.0,
      "end_time": 247481.0,
      "text": "wouldn't stop people from coming in."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 247481.0,
      "end_time": 250350.0,
      "text": "It would actually stop them from going back."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 250350.0,
      "end_time": 252386.0,
      "text": "In fact, the whole idea of building a border wall"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 252386.0,
      "end_time": 253687.0,
      "text": "is misguided."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 253687.0,
      "end_time": 256056.0,
      "text": "The Mexican economy is doing  quite well right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 256055.99999999997,
      "end_time": 258791.99999999997,
      "text": "and population growth  has slowed way down."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 258791.99999999997,
      "end_time": 260626.99999999997,
      "text": "So, there's not much  pressure to emigrate."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 260627.0,
      "end_time": 262462.0,
      "text": "The number of illegal    border crossings"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 262462.0,
      "end_time": 264965.0,
      "text": "is actually at an all-time low."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 264965.0,
      "end_time": 268368.0,
      "text": "If you're a professor, then why are you in the desert?"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 268368.0,
      "end_time": 271371.0,
      "text": "I'm not, I'm a mirage."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 271371.0,
      "end_time": 277578.0,
      "text": "(gasping)  Hey!"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 277578.0,
      "end_time": 279813.0,
      "text": "Look, we already have  what has to be the most"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 279813.0,
      "end_time": 283150.0,
      "text": "militarized border between    any two nations at peace."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 283150.0,
      "end_time": 284384.0,
      "text": "So, the real issue   of immigration"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 284384.0,
      "end_time": 286320.0,
      "text": "isn't the people coming in."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 286320.0,
      "end_time": 288488.0,
      "text": "The fact is,    they're already here."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 288488.0,
      "end_time": 291124.0,
      "text": "Nearly one out of every  30 people in America"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 291124.0,
      "end_time": 294561.0,
      "text": "is an unauthorized immigrant."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 294561.0,
      "end_time": 296997.0,
      "text": "Hm, the only thing a wall stops"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 296997.0,
      "end_time": 299533.0,
      "text": "is a discussion of actual solutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 299533.0,
      "end_time": 301168.0,
      "text": "(man speaking Spanish on TV)"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 301168.0,
      "end_time": 303403.0,
      "text": "Oh, my God,  Adam, you're right."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 303403.0,
      "end_time": 304738.0,
      "text": "The wall isn't the answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 304738.0,
      "end_time": 307107.0,
      "text": "Oh, good, I'm so glad I could help."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 307107.0,
      "end_time": 309343.0,
      "text": "Millions of people    are already here."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 309343.0,
      "end_time": 311778.0,
      "text": "We need to deport them."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 311778.0,
      "end_time": 314047.0,
      "text": "Yes! Deportation is the answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 314047.0,
      "end_time": 318852.0,
      "text": "No..."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 318852.0,
      "end_time": 328852.0,
      "text": "(gasping)    Alfonso!"
    }
  ]
